Important Reminder
The office is closed from 12:30 Sunday, Monday and Tuesday and reopens on Wed morning. Reservations will not be taken or made during this time frame nor will voice mail be answered. Email is monitored and answered periodically. If you want to ARRIVE on Sunday after 12:30, Monday or Tuesday, reservations must be made by Saturday at the latest. Sunday, Mon and Tues arrivals paperwork/map will be in the arrivals box on the office porch.
Reservations are required.
During the months of April through October reservations should be made at least a week in advance due to limited availability. We have a 2 night minimum requirement.
Jan through Mar are monthly only. November and December are subject to availability.  Please read and understand our rules prior to making a reservation.  We guarantee you a site, but reserve the right to change the assigned site due to circumstances.
The office is closed on Monday and Tuesday. On Sunday the office closes at 12:30. Email is monitored and answered periodically those days. Reservations and voice mail will not be taken care of until Wednesday.  Please plan accordingly.
During the months of January - March we have 1-3 month sites only. We don't do
short
term reservations until April.
If you are trying to book a monthly or longer site for next season, our waiting list
star
ts on 1 March 2024. Please
email
your type/length of rv, number of adults/pets and your phone number.
Repeated calling in will not expedite the process!
Thank you for your inquiry.
Please keep in mind, email is the quickest way to make a reservation. The office will get back to you about availability. Please use this method as you will get the best possible result. We appreciate your cooperation!
18701 San Carlos Blvd, Fort Myers
Beach, FL, United States, Florida 33931
(239) 466-3133
mail@sancarlosrv.com
